node.title: Nok et innlegg
node.content:
One hundred dollars. Good man. Nixon’s pro-war and pro-family. And then the battle’s not so bad? I just want to talk. It has nothing to do with mating. Fry, that doesn’t make sense. Good man. Nixon’s pro-war and pro-family.

That’s the ONLY thing about being a slave. We’re rescuing ya. Fry, we have a crate to deliver. With a warning label this big, you know they gotta be fun!

Anyone who laughs is a communist! Son, as your lawyer, I declare y’all are in a 12-piece bucket o’ trouble. But I done struck you a deal: Five hours of community service cleanin’ up that ol’ mess you caused.

Hi, I’m a naughty nurse, and I really need someone to talk to. $9.95 a minute. Why yes! Thanks for noticing. Isn’t it true that you have been paid for your testimony? In your time, yes, but nowadays shut up! Besides, these are adult stemcells, harvested from perfectly healthy adults whom I killed for their stemcells.

You guys go on without me! I’m going to go… look for more stuff to steal! I don’t know what you did, Fry, but once again, you screwed up! Now all the planets are gonna start cracking wise about our mamas.

Daylight and everything. Bender, being God isn’t easy. If you do too much, people get dependent on you, and if you do nothing, they lose hope. You have to use a light touch. Like a safecracker, or a pickpocket.

Come, Comrade Bender! We must take to the streets! You guys aren’t Santa! You’re not even robots. How dare you lie in front of Jesus? I daresay that Fry has discovered the smelliest object in the known universe!
